.DT
remove_follower
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
remove_follower

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
remove_follower -  This method removes a follower from the living object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int remove_follower(object ob)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object to remove from the follow list
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method removes a follower from the living object.  A follower will
happily follow around the person in front.  Used in the unfollow
and lose commands.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_follower(), query_followers()
.EP

